text:
──────...Ha?
Eh... I mean, why are you here...?

Ah, umm...
I didn't mean to interrupt you, but

If you want to use the lesson studio,
Please let me know...

Ah, no reason...
I just kind of had a feeling you might be here.

Ah... I guess you could hear me from below.
Sorry for being loud...

Eh?
No, you weren't being too noisy...

...
Just let me know if you want to use it, okay?
